---
description: Use this project's uv-managed .venv for all Python commands.
globs: ["**/*.py", "**/pyproject.toml", ".github/workflows/*.yml"]
alwaysApply: true
---

# UV-only execution (ShinkaEvolve)

- Run Python, pytest, ruff, mypy, black, and CLI entrypoints with **`uv run ...`** from the repo root so the interpreter is always **`.venv`** (never bare `python` / `pip` unless verifying `uv` itself).
- Install or refresh deps with **`uv sync`** (dev group is default via `[tool.uv] default-groups` in `pyproject.toml`). Use **`uv sync --all-groups`** when working on docs (mkdocs).
- Prefer **`uv add`** / **`uv remove`** to change dependencies; commit **`uv.lock`** after lock changes.
